## **1. Primary Colors (Brand / Main UI)**

| Purpose | Color | Hex |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Primary buttons / highlights | Blue | `#4A90E2` |
| Headers / Top bar | Dark Blue | `#003366` |
| Positive balance / success | Green | `#27AE60` |

---

## **2. Secondary / Accent Colors**

| Purpose | Color | Hex |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Warning / Budget overspend | Orange | `#F39C12` |
| Negative balance / expense alerts | Red | `#E74C3C` |
| Neutral / info | Light Blue | `#5DADE2` |

---

## **3. Background / Cards**

| Purpose | Color | Hex |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Main background | Off-White | `#FAFAFA` |
| Cards / containers | Light Grey | `#F2F2F2` |
| Secondary text | Grey | `#7F8C8D` |
| Dark mode background | Dark Grey | `#121212` |

---

## **4. Charts / Graphs**

| Purpose | Color | Hex |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Positive values | Green | `#2ECC71` |
| Negative values | Red | `#E74C3C` |
| Neutral / info | Blue | `#3498DB` |
| Highlight / selected | Orange | `#F39C12` |

---

### **5. Suggested Usage**

- **Header / Navbar:** Dark Blue
- **Primary Buttons:** Blue
- **Income / Positive numbers:** Green
- **Expenses / Negative numbers:** Red
- **Alerts / Budget warnings:** Orange
- **Background:** Off-White
- **Cards:** Light Grey
- **Secondary text:** Grey